cs.LG, cs.CE, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.DB 

This paper discusses machine learning for healthcare and the importance of considering the year of care and feature aggregation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning) followed by cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses healthcare practices and hospital datasets, which could place it in cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) and cs.DB (Databases).
